# Component Guidelines

## Button Components
The application uses two main button types defined in [Button.jsx](mdc:src/components/Button.jsx):

1. `ButtonPrimary` - Primary call-to-action button
   - Parameters:
     - `label` (required): Button text
     - `href` (optional): URL to navigate to
     - `target` (optional): Link target (default: _self)
     - `icon` (optional): Material icon name
     - `classes` (optional): Additional CSS classes

2. `ButtonOutline` - Secondary outline style button
   - Has the same parameters as ButtonPrimary

## CV Download
The CV download functionality is implemented in the Hero section:
- File: [Hero.jsx](mdc:src/components/Hero.jsx)
- CV file path: [Aveek-Patra-CV.pdf](mdc:public/Aveek-Patra-CV.pdf)
- Implementation: Uses ButtonPrimary with href to the PDF file

## Animation
The application uses GSAP for animations:
- Particle animations in [Hero.jsx](mdc:src/components/Hero.jsx)
- Animation is initialized in useEffect hooks
